data.name: explainLabel.Text
data.value:
The game has encountered a serious internal problem, and cannot continue. This program exists to collect few information about the crash and your computer, to help developers fix this bug.
A ZIP file will be created in few seconds, which you can then upload to Goblin Camp forums along with additional information, like what you were doing when this crash occured.
It will contain: - crash dump, containing fragments of the game memory captured at the moment of the crash - game log - your Goblin Camp configuration file, and list of installed mods - some basic information about your operating system and environment
Feel free to review it, and not include any information you deem sensitive, but we ask you to upload at least the crash dump (dump_xxxx.dmp file).
